{"title":"Person overboard from bulk carrier Jolbos with loss of 1 life","public_updated_at":"2015-01-23T10:10:01Z","details":{"body":"<p>Completed PE Summary - Jolbos  </p>\n\n<p>A short summary of the accident and action taken:</p>\n\n<table>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Registered Owner &amp; Manager:</td>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td>Trofirm Shipping Co. Ltd</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Port of registry:</td>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td>Limassol</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Flag:</td>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td>Cyprus</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Type:</td>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td>Dry Cargo Bulk carrier</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Built:</td>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td>1994</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Classification society:</td>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td>Lloyds Register</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Length overall:</td>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td>186</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Gross tonnage:</td>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td>18813.00</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Date &amp; Time</td>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td>08/01/06 12:45</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Location of incident:</td>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td>5132.9N 00259.2W</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Incident Type:</td>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td>Accident to Person</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Persons onboard:</td>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td>28 crew</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Injuries/ fatalities:</td>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td>1 fatality</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Damage/ Pollution:</td>\n      <td>&nbsp;</td>\n      <td>None</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h3 id=\"synopsis\">Synopsis</h3>\n\n<p>As the Cypriot registered bulk carrier Jolbos was leaving Newport, on 8 January 2006, two seaman were rigging a pilot ladder of the combination type. The ladder’s suspension wire failed, allowing the ladder to swing down and throw one of the seamen into the water. He was recovered by a nearby tug but, in spite of efforts to resuscitate him, was later declared dead in hospital. </p>\n\n<h3 id=\"action-taken\">Action taken</h3>\n\n<p>The Chief Inspector has written to the vessel’s owners advising them:  </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>To remind all crew of the importance of wearing appropriate safety equipment when working over the side of a vessel.   </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>To consider introducing a programme of periodic replacement of suspension wires on accommodation and pilot ladders.   </p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The Chief Inspector decided a full investigation was not appropriate in this case. </p>\n\n<hr />\n","change_history":[],"metadata":{"bulk_published":true,"date_of_occurrence":"2006-08-01","document_type":"maib_report","report_type":"completed-preliminary-examination","vessel_type":["merchant-vessel-100-gross-tons-or-over"]}},"routes":[{"path":"/maib-reports/person-overboard-from-bulk-carrier-jolbos-at-newport-wales-with-loss-of-1-life","type":"exact"}],"redirects":[],"publishing_app":"specialist-publisher","rendering_app":"government-frontend","need_ids":[],"phase":"live","analytics_identifier":null,"document_type":"maib_report","schema_name":"placeholder_specialist_document","first_published_at":"2016-02-29T09:24:10Z","base_path":"/maib-reports/person-overboard-from-bulk-carrier-jolbos-at-newport-wales-with-loss-of-1-life","description":"Location: Departing from Newport, Wales.","content_id":"66875510-6c46-4940-afaf-a797daecadf7","locale":"en","expanded_links":{"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"PC472","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/marine-accident-investigation-branch","base_path":"/government/organisations/marine-accident-investigation-branch","content_id":"9c66b9a3-1e6a-48e8-974d-2a5635f84679","description":null,"document_type":"organisation","locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2015-04-18T09:12:26Z","schema_name":"placeholder